Package: HiCociety
Type: Package
Title: HiCociety creates modules of chromatin interaction from chromatin conformation capture based data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Sora Yoon, PhD
Maintainer: Sora Yoon <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: It creates HiC network of nodes forming significant contacts, and clusters the network to create chromatin interaction modules.
    Also, it compares the connectivity of modules from two HiC dataset.
